11// RVV Extension
12constexpr Opcode OP_IVV = OP_V | (0b000 << kFunct3Shift);
13constexpr Opcode OP_FVV = OP_V | (0b001 << kFunct3Shift);
14constexpr Opcode OP_MVV = OP_V | (0b010 << kFunct3Shift);
15constexpr Opcode OP_IVI = OP_V | (0b011 << kFunct3Shift);
16constexpr Opcode OP_IVX = OP_V | (0b100 << kFunct3Shift);
17constexpr Opcode OP_FVF = OP_V | (0b101 << kFunct3Shift);
18constexpr Opcode OP_MVX = OP_V | (0b110 << kFunct3Shift);
19
20constexpr Opcode RO_V_VSETVLI = OP_V | (0b111 << kFunct3Shift) | 0b0 << 31;
21constexpr Opcode RO_V_VSETIVLI = OP_V | (0b111 << kFunct3Shift) | 0b11 << 30;
22constexpr Opcode RO_V_VSETVL = OP_V | (0b111 << kFunct3Shift) | 0b1 << 31;
